column5: Just a warning to anybody fishing Gullrock during the first week of August. There is going to be a fisherman on Gullrock that week that is " The Best". His touch with a Walleye Rod is unbelivable. I have never seen anyone catch so many fish and big fish as him. I cant tell you his name but if you see a guy that calls himself "Vant" you better look to the heavens and say ...Thank You ...I have seen "The Best"
My good friend Walli needs a real job. VANT
Vant, Thanks for keeping me in your "Friend" category. You are the best ....maybe second best when we wet a line together. CATCH AND RELEASE
